### PUT request to update allergy notes and reaction details
PUT http://localhost:4000/patients/{{patient_id}}/allergies/{{allergy_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "{{patient_id}}",
  "allergen": "Peanuts",
  "allergyType": "FOOD",
  "severity": "LIFE_THREATENING",
  "reaction": "Anaphylaxis within 5-10 minutes of exposure, severe swelling, respiratory distress, drop in blood pressure",
  "notes": "Recent testing confirmed continued severe allergy. Patient education updated on reading food labels. New EpiPen auto-injector prescribed. Emergency action plan reviewed with family.",
  "isActive": true
}

